article_id:1932,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Crossover Event, Caged Desire, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/242f2780666c88e88b512ddf0a79ceb9.png,message:<div>Caged Desire, a crossover event with the Persona series of games, starts at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span>. During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against a raid boss with no elemental attunement.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5d5096874cf29b02015e27809bdc3853.png"></div><div>Ladies and gentlemen of Dragalia Lost... The Phantom Thieves of Hearts have arrived! A sudden string of strange occurrences has rocked the continent of Grastaea. At the head of this twisted crusade stands none other than Prince Emile himself. As innocent subjects suffer under the yoke of this villain, the Prince and friends are joined by the Phantom Thieves in a rush to explore the imperial-capital-turned-Metaverse before the world as they know it is corrupted forever!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613109599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>▼Caged Desire trailer &amp; special website release!</div><div><br></div><div>A trailer and special website for Caged Desire event were released.</div><div><br></div><div>・Nintendo Mobile YouTube Channel - Caged Desire Event Trailer</div><div><a href="https://youtu.be/6BTqFiJpRQg">https://youtu.be/6BTqFiJpRQg</a></div><div><br></div><div>・Caged Desire Special Website</div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/event/persona/">https://dragalialost.com/en/event/persona/</a></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/event/persona/">https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/event/persona/</a></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>▼Events to commemorate Caged Desire!</div><div><br></div><div>1. Daily free tenfold summon!</div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, starts at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612677540"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Applicable Summon Showcase</div><div>Showcase available during the daily free tenfold summon event.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. You can perform a tenfold summon for free on the applicable summon showcase once per day (each day is from 6:00 AM to 5:59 AM the next day).</div><div>2. The daily free tenfold summon resets each day at 6:00 AM.</div><div>3. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>2. Caged Desire bonus</div><div>You can get fabulous rewards when you log in for the duration of the event!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9f833f5eb8488f6f7b4b07eab49ead5a.png"></div><div>■Log-In Bonus Content</div><div>Day 1: 5★ wyrmprint &quot;Caged Desire&quot; &times; 1</div><div>Day 2: &quot;It&#39;s showtime!&quot; sticker &times; 1</div><div>Day 3: Gold Crystal &times; 1,000</div><div>Day 4: Mana &times; 1,000,000</div><div>Day 5: Damascus Ingot &times; 1</div><div>Day 6: Otherworldly Leblanc Curry &times; 5</div><div>Day 7: Blessed Ethon Ashes &times; 5</div><div>Day 8: Sunlight Stone &times; 1</div><div>Day 9: Rupie &times; 100,000,000</div><div>Day 10: Tenfold Summon Voucher &times; 1</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613109599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Log-in bonus content (excluding the wyrmprint and sticker) will be sent to your goodie box every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.</div><div>2. Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.</div><div>3. The 5★ wyrmprint &quot;Caged Desire&quot; will be gifted directly to you instead of being sent to your goodie box.</div><div>4. Obtained stickers will be added directly to your Available Stickers.</div><div><br></div><div>3. Caged Desire upgrade events</div><div>▼Double drops and half-stamina event for certain main campaign quests</div><div>For the duration of the event, drop rewards you can obtain from chapters one through six of the main campaign will be doubled on all difficulty levels and these quests will only require half the normal amount of stamina. You can also get double the amount of draconic essences from eligible quests!</div><div><br></div><div>This is your chance to play Very Hard difficulty and get lots of Incandescence Orbs, Tsunami Orbs, Tempest Orbs, Resplendence Orbs, and Abaddon Orbs, which can be used to unlock nodes on the mana spiral!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613109599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>▼Avenue to Power double drops and Avenue to Fortune double rupies event</div><div>During this event, drop rewards you can obtain from Avenue to Power and rupies you can obtain from Avenue to Fortune will be doubled!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613109599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>▼Special adventurer upgrade event for every element</div><div>The following event, which makes it easier to upgrade adventurers of every element, will be live for the duration.</div><div><br></div><div>・Drop rewards you can obtain from Elemental Ruins of every element will be doubled.</div><div>・Drop rewards you can obtain from Dragon Trials of every element will be doubled.</div><div>・Drop rewards you can obtain from The Imperial Onslaught of every element will be doubled.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1613109599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・Events do not apply to certain drop rewards such as wyrmprints, astral pieces, fafnir medals, event items, and survival bonuses.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1611295200,update_time1611297774